        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Method",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Mix and bake, 45 to 50 minutes",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Preheat the oven to 170°C fan. Grease and line a 900 g loaf tin with baking paper. Beat the softened {{unsalted-butter}} and {{caster-sugar}} (cake amount) together until pale and fluffy, about 4 minutes. Beat in the {{eggs}} one at a time, adding a tablespoon of flour with each egg to prevent curdling. Fold in the remaining {{self-raising-flour}} and the {{lemon}} zest, then stir in the {{whole-milk}} until the batter is smooth. Pour into the tin and level the surface.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Bake for 45 to 50 minutes, until golden and a skewer inserted into the centre comes out clean. The top will crack along the length, which is correct.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Apply the drizzle",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Mix the {{lemon}} juice (drizzle amount) with the {{caster-sugar}} (drizzle amount). Do not heat or stir until dissolved. You want some sugar crystals intact. The moment the cake comes out of the oven, use a skewer to poke holes across the surface, then pour the ",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "text": "drizzle",
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "glossaryTooltip",
                "attrs": {
                  "termId": "cmpa6g4jw00000ov4hx6d18ae"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": " over the top, making sure it reaches the edges. Leave to cool in the tin until the drizzle has set, then lift out onto a rack.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
